> Dear Ankesh Pal


I acknowledge receipt of your email regarding the discontinuation of our 
recruitment services.

As per the terms of our agreement, either party may terminate the 
agreement by providing two months’ written notice. Therefore, I kindly 
request you to follow the agreed procedure and serve the notice period 
accordingly. Until the notice period is completed, I will continue to 
provide services as per our contract.

Additionally, I would request you to share detailed feedback regarding 
the candidates whose resumes were shared and finalized up to this date. 
Please specify the exact reasons why they were not selected, as all CVs 
submitted were carefully matched to the requirements and were relevant 
to the profiles discussed.

This will not only help in maintaining transparency but also enable me 
to improve the recruitment process and ensure alignment with your 
expectations during the notice period.

Looking forward to your cooperation.

Best regards,
Shohaib Jaffrey
